org.javassonne.messaging
Class Notification

java.lang.Object
  org.javassonne.messaging.Notification

public class Notification
extends java.lang.Object

The Notification class represents a single notification sent using the NotificationManager. Each notification has a few important properties: argument: an object that was passed using sendNotification identifier: in class, we referred to this as the EventType. It should be one of the static final values below.
